<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">غ ص ب:</span> <span class="c2">(الْغَصْبُ)</span> أَخْذُ الشَّيْءِ ظُلْمًا وَبَابُهُ ضَرَبَ تَقُولُ: <span class="c2">(غَصَبَهُ)</span> مِنْهُ. وَغَصَبَهُ عَلَيْهِ. وَ <span class="c2">(الِاغْتِصَابُ)</span> مِثْلُهُ. وَالشَّيْءُ <span class="c2">(غَصْبٌ)</span> وَ <span class="c2">(مَغْصُوبٌ)</span> .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>